#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn48.24:0.2"
msgid "3. Chaḷindriyavagga "
msgstr "3. The Six Faculties "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 24. Ekabījīsutta → ekābhiññaṃ (pts1)
msgctxt "sn48.24:0.3"
msgid "24. Ekabījīsutta "
msgstr "24. A One-Seeder "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.205, sc1
msgctxt "sn48.24:1.1"
msgid "“Pañcimāni, bhikkhave, indriyāni. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these five faculties. "

msgctxt "sn48.24:1.2"
msgid "Katamāni pañca? "
msgstr "What five? "

msgctxt "sn48.24:1.3"
msgid "Saddhindriyaṃ … pe … paññindriyaṃ—"
msgstr "The faculties of faith, energy, mindfulness, immersion, and wisdom. "

msgctxt "sn48.24:1.4"
msgid "imāni kho, bhikkhave, pañcindriyāni. "
msgstr "These are the five faculties. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. VAR: ekabījī → ekabīji (mr)
#. VAR: sattakkhattuparamo → sattakkhattuṃparamo (s1-3)
msgctxt "sn48.24:1.5"
msgid "Imesaṃ kho, bhikkhave, pañcannaṃ indriyānaṃ samattā paripūrattā arahaṃ hoti, tato mudutarehi antarāparinibbāyī hoti, tato mudutarehi upahaccaparinibbāyī hoti, tato mudutarehi asaṅkhāraparinibbāyī hoti, tato mudutarehi sasaṅkhāraparinibbāyī hoti, tato mudutarehi uddhaṃsoto hoti akaniṭṭhagāmī, tato mudutarehi sakadāgāmī hoti, tato mudutarehi ekabījī hoti, tato mudutarehi kolaṃkolo hoti, tato mudutarehi sattakkhattuparamo hoti, tato mudutarehi dhammānusārī hoti, tato mudutarehi saddhānusārī hotī”ti. "
msgstr "Someone who has completed and fulfilled these five faculties is a perfected one. If they are weaker than that, they’re one who is extinguished between one life and the next … one who is extinguished upon landing … one who is extinguished without extra effort … one who is extinguished with extra effort … one who heads upstream, going to the Akaniṭṭha realm … a once-returner … a one-seeder … one who goes from family to family … one who has seven rebirths at most … a follower of the teachings … a follower by faith.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn48.24:1.6"
msgid "Catutthaṃ. "
msgstr ""

